sub_title: Learn Dutch with Joy! Well trained, native Dutch teachers for expats from around the world. Private courses and small online groups.
summary:
We offer online Dutch courses with well trained, native teachers in small groups or 1 on 1. For Beginners up to C1. We focus on conversation, grammar and giving students an enjoyable time, while encouraging them to connect to their daily Dutch environment. We also offer Business Dutch and prepare for inburgering exam, state exam, AKV medical exam and CNaVT exam. And we offer Dutch courses specifically for Afrikaans speakers. Let's learn Dutch with Joy!

In our Private Courses we tailor the content, the pace and the schedule fully to your personal needs and wishes. 100% of the attention and speaking time is for you. A very efficient way to learn Dutch!

In our Group Courses, we focus on conversation, grammar and giving students an enjoyable time, while encouraging them to connect to their daily Dutch environment. Our groups are small, which gives you the joy and advantages of learning in a group as well as the benefits of personal attention.

In our Dutch classes tailored to people who speak Afrikaans, we address their advantages and challenges that cone with speaking this language with similar roots. A fast route to learning Dutch!
